| Table Type         | Description                                     | Implementation Notes |
|------------------- | ----------------------------------------------- |-------------------------------- |
| Standard Sticky    | Default table with sticky headers.              | Wrap in div with class='sticky' |
| Standard Nonsticky | Default table without sticky headers.           | Use default markdown |
| Striped Table      | Striped table with or without sticky headers    | Wrap in div with class='striped' |
| Borderless Table   | Borderless table with or without sticky headers | Wrap in div with class='borderless' |
| Scrollable Table   | Table permits scrolling data on resize          | Wrap table in div with class='scrollable-table' and tabindex='0' |
| Sortable Table     | Simple sorting for basic markdown tables        | Wrap table in div with class='simple-sorted-table' |